title: FSX Quick Map
description:
Hi there
I would like to share with you this program tested on Windows XP only, don\&#039;t know about Vista

The author said:
---------------------
QuickMap - ... an easy-to-use Moving Map for FS

FS2002/FS2004/FSX AI aircraft display 
ILS Profile Display 
Data Logging 
There\&#039;s not much to say about this program and there shouldn\&#039;t be too much to say about it... The basic idea is a very simple and effective Moving Map. One you want to use and has all it takes without being complicated and cluttered with features.  
---------------------
 
Till the new FSNav shows, I use quickmap as my FSX moving map.


Have fun!!!
